Name: Cat Box Paradox
About the game: Dead? Alive? Both? Help Einstein the cat restore reality before his owners come home to a dangerously unstable alternate dimension. In this fast paced retro platform game, you must think fast as you run, jump and swap colour, making your way through 8 floors of challenging and amusing colour changing mayhem. . Features Unique colour changing gameplay Fast, fun and challenging experience Local 2 player co-op mode (Joypad required for player 2) Assist mode 8-Bit retro inspired graphics & sound 8 floors of varied level design Secret challenge levels to unlock Hats for cats! Cat puns galore!
